title: EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Adam.Woodyatt.and.Laurie.Brett
description:
EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Adam.Woodyatt.and.Laurie.Brett

Celebrate 30 years of EastEnders in the company of those who know it best - the stars! Relive iconic moments and find out the real gossip from the set.

Adam and Laurie welcome you into their Walford home to celebrate 30 years of EastEnders. From revisiting Ian's first EastEnders appearance at it's beginnings till todays (still unresolved) crisis of Lucy's demise, Adam's been witness to it all!
